\par
Sidebars are one of the most complex components to build. They are central\par
to any application and often contain a lot of moving parts.\par
\par
We now have a solid foundation to build on top of. Composable. Themeable.\par
Customizable.\par
\par
[Browse the Blocks Library](/blocks).\par
\par
