## Styling\par
\par
Here are some tips for styling the sidebar based on different states.\par
\par
```tsx\par
<Sidebar collapsible="icon">\par
  <SidebarContent>\par
    <SidebarGroup className="group-data-[collapsible=icon]:hidden" />\par
  </SidebarContent>\par
</Sidebar>\par
```\par
\par
```tsx\par
<SidebarMenuItem>\par
  <SidebarMenuButton />\par
  <SidebarMenuAction className="peer-data-[active=true]/menu-button:opacity-100" />\par
</SidebarMenuItem>\par
```\par
